  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Globalt Fokus - Claim Your Space - 2021-2022</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">From 2021 to 2022, the CYS would provide two tracks of activities:

1. Emergency assistance funds to individuals and groups under threat
2. Grants to locally-led activities to proactively counter restrictions to civic space

These two tracks of activities would make CYS a unique effort in its efforts to combine emergency rapid response support with a proactive and sustainable response to closing civic space. The sustainability is reached through local ownership and broad alliances for civic space. Ideally, the track 2 will enhance local responses to crises situations before emergency funding through track 1 is necessary.</narrative>
  </description>
